      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "ryg4Fgr9hX",
      "rebuttal_id": "Bkggfq0VTm",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "text": "Nevertheless, although the experimental increases might not seem dramatic, they are statistically significant (we have added the statistical significance results to the appendix in the revised version).",
